# https://github.com/grafana/security-docs/blob/main/docs/appsec/security-tools/trufflehog.md#per-repo-exclusions-trufflehogignore

# Vendored Yarn 4 release binary — minified JS containing config option names
# like `npmPublishProvenance` that trip TruffleHog's GitLab token detector.
# Integrity is enforced by the pinned release in .yarnrc.yml (`yarnPath`) and
# `checksumBehavior: throw` in .yarnrc.yml; version is pinned in package.json
# `packageManager`.
.yarn/releases/.*\.cjs$
